               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480228-name-1235" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1235" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1235" type="surname" value="DOOLEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1235" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN DOOLEY.</persName>
                  </hi> I am a publican, at 61, Old Bailey. I missed this pewter pot about 11th Jan. (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—I believe I had seen it safe that day.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480228-name-1236" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1236" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1236" type="surname" value="WILD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1236" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WILD</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, M</hi> 94.) I received information, and went to a house in Hope-place, Borough-road—the prisoner lodged at the top of the house—I saw the landlord, and waited till the prisoner came home at past eleven o'clock at night; and when he opened his room door I walked in after him—he tried to prevent me, but I got in and found two pots—I took him in charge, and on the following morning I found this pot there is a hamper, under a lot of things—he said some one had put it into his room, or I had put it there myself.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What time were you there? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I had information three days before I went to the house—when you got in, you said, "Good God, I wish I was out of the place"—I said, "I am a constable"—you said, "I thought it was my landlord"—you showed me the room—you did not tell my where the pot was to go.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480228-name-1237" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1237" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1237" type="surname" value="LEECH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480228-name-1237" type="given" value="MARY ANN"></interp>MARY ANN LEECH.</persName>
                  </hi> I saw the prisoner bend up pots between two pieces of rag on the night before he was taken.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The landlord look the house where I reside, and next day he gave me notice to quit; it did not suit me to move, and he had annoyed me in every way; he took away some furniture of mine and gave me no account of it, and then I was charged with pot-stealing; I was at the Auction<lb></lb>mart, and never went home till past eleven o'clock; I could not have taken this pot.</p>
